# Pulse App – Updated Project Plan

## Summary
Pulse is a real-time, asymmetric event web app where:
- An **Admin** creates and hosts an event.
- Users join via **automatically generated QR code / room code**.
- Users appear as **dots in a shared lobby**.
- A timed **game loop** displays questions.
- Users vote anonymously.
- Results are visualized live and summarized.

---

## Core Features (MVP)

### Admin
- Register / Login 
- Create Event (name, theme)
- Auto-generate **unique room code + QR**
- Choose **question category** from **pre-defined question sets** (pulled from database or external API)
- Option to **write custom questions**
- Configure:
  - Question duration
  - Result duration
  - Lobby delay (time between questions)
- Display live lobby (connected users shown as dots)
- Start / Pause / Stop game loop
- View and control game from:
  - Large screen (event screen)
  - Mobile (admin control panel)
---

### User
- Join via QR / code
- Enter username
- Lobby view (participants as floating dots)
- Receive questions in real-time when game is active
- Submit one answer per question (anonymous) via buttons
- Confirmation animation on vote
- Automatically return to lobby after answering

---

## Real-time Behavior (Clarified)

- Users joining/leaving update instantly in lobby
- When a user votes:
  → A dot appears **immediately** in the selected answer section on the main screen
- Dots:
  - Are anonymous
  - Are randomly positioned within their answer section
  - Represent a single vote each
- Timer is synchronized across all devices
- Game loop runs continuously unless paused by admin

---

## Game Loop Logic (Updated)

1. Admin starts game
2. Question appears on:
   - User devices
   - Event screen
3. Timer starts (e.g. 5 minutes)
4. Users vote
   - Votes instantly render as dots in correct section on large screen
   - Users who has voted return to "lobby" view with 
5. Timer reaches 0
6. Results screen shown:
   - % per answer 
   - user dots are rendered in the background (with name and avatar (If we implement it))
7. Short delay (still result screen) (e.g. 5 minutes)
8. Countdown to next question appears on result screen (30 seconds to next question)
8. Next question loads automatically
9. Loop repeats

### Admin Controls During Game
- Pause loop at any time
- Resume loop
- Adjust timers live
- Change next question
- Control everything from mobile device

